  it.

*sed-3.02.80-r3.ebuild (23 Aug 2002)

  23 Aug 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> sed-3.02.80-r3.ebuild :

  Forced upgrade, so that people who got clobbered by supersed, will now
  install this again.

